  "body": "Noticing high seq no's in the topaz testnet due to frequent `attnets` field updates.  I believe this is due to confusion regarding whether or not the `attnets` field in the ENR should be updated for only persistent committee changes.  \r\n\r\nI suggested that a clarification should be made in the spec.  I believe @djrtwo is considering something like:\r\n\r\n> Note: Short lived beacon committee assignments should not translate into updating attnets field in the ENR\r\n\r\nCC: @nisdas ",
